text: Þis his þære VI hida boc æt langanforde þe eadwig cing gebocode byrnrice his þegne on eche yrfe.
Þis synt þa land gemæra to langanforde.
Ærest of þare ea on east cumb.
Of æs dune to puntes stane þonon andlang grimes dic to hunan wege to þam stane.
Þonon on þone to brocenan beorh.
Þonon adune andlang weges on þone lytlan to brocenan beorh.
